  m_Name: NeighborJournal_21
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 41
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #21 \u2014 B\u1EE9c th\u01B0 cu\u1ED1i"
  category: 3
  content: "T\xF4i vi\u1EBFt thay cho nhi\u1EC1u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi m\u1EB9 trong chung
    c\u01B0 n\xE0y. B\xE0 Hoa t\u1EA7ng 8 \u2014 g\u1EEDi con g\xE1i \u1EDF M\u1EF9:
    'Con \u01A1i, m\u1EB9 y\xEAu con, \u0111\u1EEBng v\u1EC1, th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 kh\xF4ng
    c\xF2n an to\xE0n.' B\xE0 Lan t\u1EA7ng 12 \u2014 g\u1EEDi con trai \u1EDF \u0110\xE0
    N\u1EB5ng: 'M\u1EB9 kh\xF4ng ti\u1EBFc g\xEC, ch\u1EC9 ti\u1EBFc kh\xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    \xF4m con l\u1EA7n cu\u1ED1i.' B\xE0 Nguy\u1EC7t t\u1EA7ng 15 \u2014 g\u1EEDi
    ch\u1ED3ng: 'Anh h\xE3y s\u1ED1ng v\xEC con.' Ch\xFAng t\xF4i vi\u1EBFt v\xEC
    hy v\u1ECDng ai \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c s\u1EBD mang tin v\u1EC1 cho
    con c\xE1i ch\xFAng t\xF4i. Xin h\xE3y n\xF3i v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng r\u1EB1ng m\u1EB9
    ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 ngh\u0129 v\u1EC1 ch\xFAng \u0111\u1EBFn gi\xE2y cu\u1ED1i
    c\xF9ng."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
